{"tid":2346823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫委會三個醫生直選委員由「開明派」當選","createTime":"2020-12-30T13:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T13:54:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d75358204f6fc6fa59b46821820de97f3681955","tid":2346823,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】醫委會三個醫生直選委員席位，由被視為「開明派」的三人當選。<br />\n<br />\n醫委會完成點票，醫學會副會長鄭志文成功連任，新加入的有公共醫療醫生協會會長馬仲儀及醫學會會董覃天笙，三人各得3000多票，麻醉科專科醫生韋玉珍連任失敗，外籍眼科專科醫生馬思特落敗，兩人各得票1000多。<br />\n<br />\n三席由全體醫生選出，任期由下月24日起為期三年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418496&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=85e25dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418496&h=d34f0ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418496</a>"},{"pid":"c36381055ea9b4932f1f3eb4729774d880b61e27","tid":2346823,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ea68206e1a0d798b60cf53216575fc9741891a","tid":2346823,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"香港得番醫學界叫做守得住<br />\n不過都頂唔到好耐"}]}